# 📄 Smart AI PDF Analyzer (Gemini)

Smart AI PDF Analyzer is a Streamlit-based web app that allows users to upload PDF files, extract text, and ask AI-powered questions about the content using **Google Gemini 2.5 Pro**.  
It’s a clean, modern, and interactive way to understand and summarize any PDF document.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 📂 Upload any PDF file
- 🔍 AI-powered content analysis using **Gemini 2.5 Pro**
- 🧠 Ask natural language questions about your PDF
- 💬 Get intelligent, contextual answers instantly
- 🎨 Modern UI with gradient background and styled buttons
- 🧱 Built using **Streamlit**, **PyPDF2**, and **Google Generative AI**

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Component      | Technology            |
| -------------- | --------------------- |
| Frontend       | Streamlit             |
| Backend        | Python                |
| AI Model       | Google Gemini 2.5 Pro |
| PDF Processing | PyPDF2                |

---

